{"tid":2158122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美卿轉抵波蘭 簽署國防合作協議","createTime":"2020-08-15T13:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T15:58:58.000Z","uid":277037,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"69659be8f51fd9bdf15268c07d293135e7f9e41e","tid":2158122,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧抵達波蘭，展開歐洲四國訪問行程的最後一站，與總理莫拉維茨基會談，討論新型肺炎疫情、5G網絡建設、白俄羅斯局勢、發展能源計劃等議題。蓬佩奧又與波蘭國防部長簽署國防合作協議，為部份駐德國美軍，重新部署到波蘭鋪平道路。根據去年的雙邊決定，美國將會向波蘭增派1000名美軍，令駐當地美軍人數增至5500人。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-15 21:30:10<br />\nSource:RTHK"},{"pid":"f262d696b5c3bd6294a535d15713c6a631b8794b","tid":2158122,"uid":277037,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"人哋美國周圍拉攏緊盟友，支那仲係到拎緊香港黎出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9437bb249a604c7de2a439ffe022c54fa59abcb4","tid":2158122,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f86e47092c68674d89db48652197f0309d9088","tid":2158122,"uid":277037,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRNXwHY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRNXwHY.gif&h=7ba2f42a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36548b74124f1c90a46d15ad8a4c9aa4eb485e2c","tid":2158122,"uid":166405,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"波蘭呢d咪醒目仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n德國肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605384a6d50d10d29186bc6573e9f4d53df3278c","tid":2158122,"uid":277037,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy